Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something kinda surprising just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so from here on, I wanna share some messages from our listeners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First up, we got a message from Happy Name AR!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Dare-chan, good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fan from overseas and I'm studying Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to hearing Sayuri-san's voice every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love your radio show and the fun segments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As a grad student in a doctoral program, I'm researching new cancer treatments and drugs using AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This research is super rewarding and I'm really enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to ask Sayuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to go to university after high school, what field would you want to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing! And from overseas, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I speaking proper Japanese, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to remember words like 'yabai', you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't need to remember phrases like 'yabai' or 'yabai jan'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, using AI for cancer treatments and drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I actually didn't go to university, but when I was in my first and second year of high school, I was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested in going to a university for psychology. My future dreams were still kinda vague back then, I wasn't dead set on one thing. But yeah, I really wanted to be a school counselor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was interested around my first and second year of high school. When you look up school counselors, it always says you need to study psychology or related fields. So I vaguely thought it'd be cool to study something like that back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you decide to become a school counselor and go into psychology, you might suddenly find another path interesting while you're in university. I know a lot of people around me who were thinking of going into psychology. I feel like psychology is a pretty broad field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At least when I looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, this might be more for a vocational school or college, but I was super interested in hair and makeup. I really loved makeup, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I looked into vocational schools for hair and makeup. I don't know all the details, but many schools teach both hair and makeup together. I love makeup, but I'm absolutely terrible at hair styling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even do my own hair, let alone someone else's. My hands are just so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even though I really wanted to go, I figured it'd probably be impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gave up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just thought, 'I probably can't do this.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was super interested, but even now, I still love makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah, keep up the great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, Happy Na-
